item.title: Sentiment Analysis of Mahabharata using F#
item.description: This article is part of FSAdvent 2016 calendar. This my second post of 2016. Sadly not much of writing this year. So, I need to cover up by this little longish post. So, grab your favorite coffee / tea before getting started. There is one wonderful coincidence here that both post of 2016 is based on Epic Mahabharata. If anyone interested in poem like things do check out my another post.
